document_data.name: Archive Annex
document_data.mainbody: The '''Archive Annex''' was a library found in the city of [[Neverwinter]] during the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]].{{Cite document/Before the Storm}}
document_data.Interior: The upper levels of the repository were closed off to many of its patrons, though staff were permitted to retrieve books from within and lend at their discretion.
document_data.Services: It was overseen by a stern, [[blue dragon|blue]] [[dragonborn]] librarian, who belittled some of the library's patrons.
document_data.History: Sometime during or before the {{YearlinkName|1481}},{{Stormwreck-time}} a [[hill dwarf]] [[cleric]] of [[Marthammor Duin]] came into the Archive Annex, looking for more information about an island that appeared to them in a dream.
